{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第14章中，叶开与崔玉真深入交谈，揭示了玉箫的阴谋：他利用摄心术控制丁灵琳，意图借丁灵琳之手杀死叶开。叶开推断玉箫可能是魔教四大天王之一，并透露自己的母亲曾是魔教大公主，因此他对魔教之毒有天然抗性。随后，伊夜哭突然出现，揭露了玉箫与他演戏欺骗叶开的真相，并威胁叶开交出上官小仙。叶开亮出小李探花一脉相传的飞刀，伊夜哭虽不屑一顾，却被叶开一刀封喉，命丧当场。本章通过对话层层推进，展现了玉箫的阴险、叶开的智慧与飞刀的威力，同时为魔教线索埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你占了人家的屋子，又占了人家的床，人家回来了，什么话都不说，只不过叫你让开，你都不肯，这未免太不像话了吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "她不是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "对了，我本来就不是人，我是个活神仙，无论你藏到什么地方去，我还是一找就找到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是我倒真没有想到，这位道士姑娘会把你弄到这么样一个好地方，要不是她急着替你去抓药，这次我真的差点找不到你了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜她实在不能算是个好大夫，这种药你就算喝八百斤下去，也一样没有用。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你能治好他的伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我也不是个好大夫，可是我却替他请了个最好的大夫来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这位就是昔年妙手神医的惟一传人\"妙手郎中\"华子清，你见多识广，想必一定知道他的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "想不到阁下非但医道高明，而且还很会作戏。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这点你就不懂，要学偷，就一定要学会作戏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为你一定要学会扮成各式各样的人，才能到各种地方去偷各式各样的东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "譬如说，你若要到庙里去偷经，就一定得扮成和尚，若要去偷窑子，就一定要扮成嫖客。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "你若要到大字号的店家去偷，就一定得先扮成大老板的样子去踩道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "阁下当真是举一反三，一点就透，若要学这一行，我敢保证不出三个月，就可以成为专家。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "他现在就已经是专家了，所以你去替他治伤的时候，最好小心点，否则你说不定反而会被他给偷得干干净净。",
      "tone": "嫣然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我偷人家已偷了几十年，能被别人偷一次，倒也有趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只要刀上没有毒，我也敢保证，不出三天，阁下就又可以去杀别人了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "speaker_name": "华子清",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "还等什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_hua_zi_qing",
      "text": "我怎么知道你是真的来替他治伤的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这位道士姑娘倒真是个细心的人，只可惜脑筋却有点不太清楚，莫非是已经被我们这位叶公子迷晕了头。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "随便你怎么说，我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "现在我若要杀他，简直比吃豆腐还容易，我何必费这么大的事？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "据说东海玉箫会采补，可是你身上倒还很结实，看来你对付男人想必也很有一套。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这本是女人值得骄傲的事，有什么好难为情的，几时有空，说不定我也要跟你学两手。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "滚出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你叫谁滚出去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我好心好意的请了人来替你治伤，你却叫我滚出去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不错，我叫你滚出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你难道不怕我杀了你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你以为你真的能杀我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你也不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只想提醒你一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我本来不愿杀人的，可是你最好莫要逼我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你现在还能杀人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你想试试？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "难道你不想你的伤快好？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只想要你滚出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不会滚，我走出去行不行？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有件事我差点忘了告诉你。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "什么事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你想不想知道那位丁姑娘现在的下落？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她现在正和郭定在一起，也跟你们一样，睡在一张床上。",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你为什么要在我面前说这种话，你明知没有用的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不信他们会做这种事？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们本来也许会对你很忠实的，可是，假如丁姑娘也冷得要命，郭定也像这位道士姑娘一样好心呢？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "假如丁姑娘身上有个见不得人的地方，中了什么毒针，郭定为了救她，是不是会替她吮出来呢？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "劫难逃过第一次，就算又逃过第二次，还有第三次，第四次，只要你不死，你就得时时刻刻的提防着，所以你就算活着，也休想过一天安稳的日子。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不在乎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我很在乎，也很怕。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "幸好你将我的刀放在枕下，幸好她没有试。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你刚才根本无力伤她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这把刀并不是只用手就可以发出去的，要用全身所有的精神和力量，才能发出一刀，可是我现在……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我知道你是为了我，才赶她走的，可是你何必为了我冒这种险……我本就是个应该受侮辱的人。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "没有人应该受侮辱，也没有人有权侮辱别人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他老人家传授我这柄刀，只是为了要我让天下的人都明白这道理，而且莫要忘记。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我想他老人家一定是个子不起的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他自己常说他只不过是个很平凡的人，可是他做的事，却是绝没有任何人能做得到的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在我只担心一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你担心她会将我的下落告诉别人，你担心她还会再回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "她绝不会这么样做的，她只希望我的伤快好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为她要我去替她对付别人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那天她故意将玉箫引去找我，为的就是要我跟他火并，她还希望我去替她杀郭定，杀伊夜哭，杀所有可能会挡住她路的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是，她也一定知道，你绝不会去替她杀人的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我虽然不会去替她杀那些人，但是那些人却一定要来杀我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只要你们拼起来，无论谁胜谁负，她都可以渔翁得利。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "所以她并不希望我受伤，更不希望我这么快就死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "所以有件事我更想不通。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "逼着你到冷香园去吹箫的那个人，可能就是玉箫派去的。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他为什么要做这种事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为他早已知道你是个本性很善良的人，早已知道你对他不满，已经想离开他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "最近我的确总在想法子避着他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他也知道我一定会到冷香园去找，所以他故意要你在那里等，故意让你将丁灵琳的下落透露给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "难道他故意想要你去将丁姑娘救出来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为他已用摄心术一类的邪法，控制了丁灵琳，叫丁灵琳一看见我就杀了我。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不错，所以他故意在那屋子的窗外，摆了三盆腊梅，为的就是要让你容易找到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "但他为了怕我疑心，所以也不能让我有容易得手的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以他又故意弄了那么多玄虚，让你永远想不到这一点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他将丁灵琳劫走，根本就不是为了上官小仙，而是为了要我的命。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我以前实在不知道他也是个这么阴险恶毒的人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "但他却绝不是金钱帮的人，因为上官小仙并不想要我死，也并不知道他用的这一着，所以我大为想不通。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "想不通什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "想不通他怎么也会摄心术这一类邪法的。",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "会这种邪术的人很少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "会的人并不少，可是真正精通的人却没有几个，其中大多数是魔教中的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "魔教？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你也听说过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我始终以为那只不过是传说而已，想不到这世上竟真的有魔教。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你没有听玉箫谈起过魔教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你跟着他已有多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "快两年了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这两年来他平时都在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他有条很大的海船，平时他都在船上，但每隔一两个月，都会找个海口停泊，补充粮食和清水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是几个月前，他却在一个没有人的荒岛上停留了六七天，没有带别的人去，也不许我们下船。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我本就在怀疑，却一直不敢相信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "怀疑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "怀疑玉箫也人了魔教，而且是魔教中的四大天王之一。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的伤口疼不疼了",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "据说魔教用的刀都有毒。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "刀上若有毒，你的伤口竟只有痛？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "刀上就是有毒，也毒不死我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为我是个奇怪的人，我的血里有种抗毒之力，尤其可以消灭魔教的毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这是天生的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "是最近才有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "怎么会有的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我的母亲，昔年本是魔教中的大公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "现在她只不过是个很平凡的老妇人，正在一个宁静的地方，安享她的余年，希望她的儿子能时常回去看看她。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是你却很少回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为她还有个儿子在陪着她。这个儿子虽不是她亲生的，却比我这个亲生的儿子更孝顺。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他长得也跟你一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他跟我不一样，他是个很奇怪的人，但却比我好看，废话也没有我这么多，我希望以后能常见他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也希望能见到他，他既然是你的兄弟，那么一定也是个很好的人。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "傅红雪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "粥煮好了没有，快添三大碗给我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "unknown",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你醒的虽不早，倒真巧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你若再迟醒片刻，只怕就永远也不会醒了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "你来得虽不巧，倒真早。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "早起的雀儿吃食，晚起的雀儿吃屎，我若非起得早，又怎么会凑巧看见那个背叛了师门的女叛徒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "看来起得太早也不是好事，她若非起得早，又怎么会撞见鬼？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那只怪你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "怪我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她若非已被你迷住了，又怎么会一大早就起来，溜回那客栈去替你打听韩贞的消息？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她算准玉箫一定已走了，却想不到我居然还留在那里。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "那天晚上他没有杀了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你以为他真要杀了我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "不是真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我们只不过是在作戏，特地作给你看的，好让你有机会去救人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "那时你们已发现我在外面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你们一进了那院子，他就已知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "看来我倒低估了他。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他也低估了你，他认为你已死定了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我知道要你这种人死，并不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "这次你总算没有看错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但现在你若不将上官小仙交出来，还是死定了。",
      "tone": "威胁",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "这次你看错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你最好明白一件事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我喜欢杀人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "这是实话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我最想杀的人就是你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "这也是实话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你若不赶快将上官小仙交出来，我绝不会再等的，我宁可不要她，也要杀了你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "你最好也明白一件事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也让你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "我不喜欢杀人，但你这种人却是例外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在你能杀得了我？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "我不能，它能。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "我只希望你莫要逼我杀你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我认得这柄刀。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "认得最好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜你不是小李探花。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你现在只不过是个受了伤的废物，你这把刀连条狗都杀不死。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "text": "这柄刀不杀狗，只杀人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ye_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊夜哭",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我倒要试试它能不能杀得死我。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    }
  ],
